31
00:01:29,568 --> 00:01:31,010
and other tools of trade.

32
00:01:31,210 --> 00:01:33,430
Such as these blue barrels. 

33
00:01:33,630 --> 00:01:35,975
These are capital costs. 

34
00:01:36,175 --> 00:01:39,167
In contrast to these capital costs
