35
00:01:39,367 --> 00:01:40,773
or only every few years

36
00:01:40,973 --> 00:01:43,604
operational maintenance costs incure
more regularly

37
00:01:43,804 --> 00:01:45,584
often on day to day basis

38
00:01:45,784 --> 00:01:48,784
for operation and maintenance
of different faecal sludge management

39
00:01:48,984 --> 00:01:50,271
services.

40
00:01:50,509 --> 00:01:52,938
Let us consider again
our previous example.

41
00:01:53,138 --> 00:01:55,346
What would be operational
maintenance cost

