are examples for operational
maintenance costs.

45
00:02:05,134 --> 00:02:07,778
Replacing of personal production
equipment

46
00:02:07,978 --> 00:02:09,129
or cleaning supplies

47
00:02:09,329 --> 00:02:11,823
or paying of a discharge fee
at a treatment plant

48
00:02:12,023 --> 00:02:13,420
are examples.

49
00:02:13,620 --> 00:02:16,995
In this case the pickup is least
and the rent for the pickup

50
00:02:17,195 --> 00:02:19,511
and additional operation cost.

51
00:02:19,711 --> 00:02:22,936
Next to this example of this
collection service provider in Kampala

